Problem :- MERCHANT'S GUIDE TO THE GALAXY
-----------------------------------------

Code :-
-------
For this assignment, I have created a Substance class. Metal, Dirt class are inheriting from that class which has two attributes name & value. The objects of these classes are immutable.

I have created a Seperator class, whose job is to seperate Metal & Dirt.

RomanToArabic class converts Roman numeral to Arabic numeral(Integer).

ObjectPriceCalculator class calculated the price of the object.

Testing :-
----------
For testing, I have used rspec.